PLACEHOLDER_FAQ_TITLE: Frequently Asked Questions About Our Dog Walking Service
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our app connects you with local, vetted dog walkers. Simply schedule a walk, track your dog's route in real-time, and receive a detailed report after each walk.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: What safety measures are in place?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: All our dog walkers undergo thorough background checks and training. We also provide insurance coverage for every walk and use GPS tracking for added security.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: How do I pay for walks?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Payment is handled securely through the app. You can pay per walk or choose a subscription plan for regular walks at a discounted rate.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: What if I need to cancel a walk?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: We understand plans change. You can cancel a scheduled walk up to 2 hours before the start time without any charge. Late cancellations may incur a small fee.

FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Everything you need to know about our dog walking service
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: How does your dog walking app work?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our app connects dog owners with trusted local dog walkers. Simply create a profile for your dog, select your preferred walking times, and book a walker with just a few taps.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: Are your dog walkers experienced and vetted?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: Yes, all our dog walkers undergo a thorough background check and are experienced in handling various dog breeds and temperaments. We also provide ongoing training to ensure the highest quality of care.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: What if I need to cancel a scheduled walk?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: We understand plans change. You can cancel a scheduled walk up to 2 hours before the start time without any cancellation fee. For last-minute cancellations, a small fee may apply.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: How long are the typical dog walks?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: We offer flexible walking durations to suit your dog's needs. Standard options include 15, 30, and 60-minute walks, but you can also request custom durations for your furry friend.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: Can I track my dog's walk in real-time?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: Absolutely! Our app features real-time GPS tracking, allowing you to follow your dog's route during the walk. You'll also receive a summary report with photos after each walk is completed.
